title: Too Wholesome? Or Not Wholesome enough?
itunes:title: Too Wholesome? Or Not Wholesome enough?
description:
Anthony and Gregg reflect on a time when nobody wanted to live with them during college and also go over their best finishing move- wrestling, that is. What is more wholesome than dancing dinosaurs?
